               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Māmās "Vita of Māmās" (fols. 4ra-29ra) 
 II) Taʾammǝra Māmās
                     "Miracles of Māmās": 13 miracles (fols. 29ra-43rb) 
 III) Malkǝʾa Māmās
                     "Image of Māmās" (fols. 43rb-46vb)
 IV) ʾƎgziʾo taśāhalanna... "O Lord,
                     have mercy on us..." (Litany for the Holy Week) (በስመ፡”…ወይበሉ፡ ካህናት፡ ዘንተ፡ አዕለታተ፡
                     በሰሙነ፡ ሕማማት፡ በኵሉ፡ ሰዓታት፡ ወእምድህረ፡ ወንጌል፡ ወእምቅድመ፡ ኪርያ፡ ላይሶን...ጸልዩ፡ በእንተ፡ ጽንዓ፡ ዛቲ፡
                     መካን...) (fols. 48va-52rb)
 V) Taʾammǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus”: 1
                     miracle (fols. 52rb-56va)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
