               <history>
                  <origin>
                     <origPlace>
                        <placeName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/INS0091AQM">ʾAgarhǝse ʾAbuna Māmās</placeName>
                     </origPlace>
                     <origDate notBefore="1931" notAfter="1932">Additio 1 states that daǧǧāzmāč
                        Walda Gabrǝʾel donated the book in 1924 A.M. (= 1931/32 A.D.), in the time
                        of King Ḫāyla Śǝllāse I (r. 1930-74) and lǝʿul rās Gugsa ʾArʾaya (d. 1933,
                        EAE II, 905-06).</origDate>
                  </origin>
                  <provenance>According to Additio 1, the Ms. was donated
                     to the church by daǧǧāzmāč Walda Gabrǝʾel. He
                     is mentioned in the supplication formulas throughout the Ms., as well as his
                     mother Walatta ʾAnanya and his father Takla Mikāʾel.</provenance>
               </history>
